  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.obsidian_weapon": "An Obsidian Block infused with §5Herobrine§r's power.\n§6Right-click§r to launch a chain of Obsidian.\n§6Weapon More Attack§r to summon a wall of Obsidian.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.shadow_obsidian_weapon": "A Shadow Obsidian Block infused with §5Herobrine§r's power.\n§6Right-click§r to launch a chain of Shadow Obsidian.\n§6Weapon More Attack§r to summon a wall of Shadow Obsidian.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.bedrock_weapon": "Forged from §7the hardest block§r known to exist.\nNo one knows how §5Herobrine§r obtained it.\nCan mine anything and may stun enemies on hit.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.shadow_obsidian_sword": "One of the §5Shadow Herobrine§r's weapon.\nCombine it with a Diamond Helmet or Diamond Chestplate in the Smithing Table, using a Netherite Upgrade Smithing Template, to craft the §5Herobrine Obsidian Diamond Armor§r.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.shadow_obsidian_pillar": "One of the §5Shadow Herobrine§r's weapon.\n§6Right-click§r to launch a chain of Shadow Obsidian Pillar.\n§6Weapon More Attack§r to summon a wall of Shadow Obsidian Pillar.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.herobrine_ender_eye": "An Ender Eye infused with §5Herobrine§r's power\n§7(While in your inventory)§r\n§6More Weapon Attack§r when not holding this weapon to shoot 3 Shadow Obsidian Pillars.\n§6More Weapon Attack§r when holding this weapon to activate Shadow Obsidian Machine Gun.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.demoniac_voltage_reaver_blade": "A fragment of the Demoniac Voltage Reaver, forged from a magnetic alloy of iron and blended obsidian.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.demoniac_voltage_reaver_fragment": "A shattered fragment of the Demoniac Voltage Reaver, forged from a magnetic alloy of iron and blended obsidian.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.demoniac_voltage_reaver_hilt": "The hilt of the Demoniac Voltage Reaver, forged from blended obsidian.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.ender_glaive": "One of §5Herobrine§r's legendary weapons.\n§aNormal Form§r: A standard glaive with no special powers. After 5 successful hits, the weapon transforms into the §5Second Form§r.\n§5Second Form§r: Lasts for 10 seconds.\n- Grants §dMOVEMENT SPEED§r and §9DAMAGE BOOST§r.\n- Press MORE WEAPON ATTACK KEY to trigger an explosion. Recharge after every 3 successful hits while in §5Second Form§r.\n§7(Current Combo Attack: ",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.ender_slayer_scythe": "One of §5Herobrine§r's legendary weapons.\n§aNormal Form§r: A normal scythe with no special powers. After 15 successful hits, it awakens into its §5Second Form§r.\n§5Second Form§r: Lasts for 30 seconds.\n- Grants §9JUMP BOOST§r, and §dDAMAGE BOOST§r effects.\n- Summons a baby Ender Dragon that fires a tiny thunder beam every 6 seconds at any target that hurts or is hurt by the player.\n- If no valid target exists, it attacks a random nearby entity.\n§7(Current Combo Attack: ",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.demoniac_voltage_reaver": "One of §5Herobrine§r's legendary weapons.\n§aNormal Form§r: A basic greatsword with no special abilities.\n§eAwakened Form§r: Shift + right-click to swap forms. After 5 successful hits, the weapon transforms into the §5Second Form§r.\n§5Second Form§r: Unleashes a chain of Snake Blades that track enemies in a wide area, dealing damage, stunning, and knocking them back.\n§7(Current Combo Attack: ",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.obsidian_sledgehammer": "One of §5Herobrine§r's legendary weapons.\n§aNormal Form§r: A normal hammer with no special powers. After 10 successful hits, it awakens into its §5Second Form§r.\n§5Second Form§r: Lasts for 10 seconds.\n- Grants §9JUMP BOOST§r and §dMOVEMENT SPEED§r effects.\n- Each ground slam summons a ring of shadow obsidian spikes from the ground.\n- The spikes knock enemies back and force them into a knocked-down state.\n§7(Current Combo Attack: ",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.ender_aegis": "One of §5Herobrine§r's legendary weapons.\n§aNormal Form§r: A standard shield with no special powers. After 5 perfect parries, it awakens into its §5Second Form§r.\n§5Second Form§r: Lasts for 10 seconds.\n- Grants §dREGENERATION§r, §eABSORPTION§r, and §9DAMAGE RESISTANCE§r.\n- Each successful parry fires a blast at your attacker, dealing damage.\n- Normal hits inflict §7WEAKNESS§r, §7SLOWNESS§r, §7DARKNESS§r, and the §5HEROBRINE§r effect.\n§7(Current Combo Attack: ",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.null_weapon": "One of §5Null§r's power.\n§6Shift Right-click§r to release, returns to your inventory after 30 seconds.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.compressessed_diamond": "Compressed Diamond: Highest Quality, Maximum Hardness",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.woopie_the_sword": "A special weapon that can unleash a skill by right-clicking while sprinting after hitting an enemy.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.diamond_shear": "Right-click to clear all effects from enemy.",
  "tooltip.annoyingvillagers.legendary_sword": "One of the Legendary Weapons.",
